bhakta kanakadasa ( kannada : ಭಕ ತ ಕನಕದಾಸ ) is a 1960 indian kannada language film directed by y. r. swamy .   it depicts the spiritual journey of kanakadasa was a devotee of the hindu deity krishna , and a poet belonging to the dasa sect .   the film stars rajkumar , krishnakumari , udaykumar in major roles .   this film , officially marked the 100th production of kannada cinema , since its inception in 1934 .   boasting of lilting tunes including the works of kanakadasa himself , the songs were held in high esteem .